1. The advanced setting changes to the video setting, shakes the head speed to put the basic setting
2. Display the wifi signal strength (some devices suppoet)
3. Increase the equipment prompt sound switch
4. Increase the day and night conversion sensitivity settings (10 infrared lights directly open (into the evening mode) 0 Infrared lights directly off (into the daytime mode))
5. Mobile image or video of a single open after the long press pop-up share and save the Local album button
6. Video playback of ordinary video and alarm video change to check box

Update
1.ios13 interface problem adaptation;
2. Cloud service status display optimization;

Update
1. About the device interface, add the device software version release status display;
2. The ball machine increases the function of the PTZ rotation;
3. Add new device cat's eye door lock;
4. The door lock has a 90 degree rotation function;
5. Support humanoid detection function;
6.Bug fixes and performance improvements；
Recently Updated
1. Support zoom function for some camera;
2. Add prompts that H265 video can not share ;
3. Add user name length limit when registering;
4. Support Smart Camera;

Update
1. Increase the number of countries supported by SMS verification;
2. Other feedback bug fixes and feature optimizations;
Recently Updated
1. There are occasional overlap problems on the device interface;
2. Some device preview interface adds zoom function;

Update
1.iOS9.0-iOS9.2 crash bug fixed；
Recently Updated
1. Add smart doorbell configure feature
2. Improve the push service
3. Support the snchronous function of daylight saving time
4. Support the function of account cancellation
5. Low-power device support
6. Time zone setting problem modification
7. Fixed the problem loss of information such as automatic login of the user when the capacity of the mobile phone disk is low;
